WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to the fever care guide.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:12.000
Monitor your child's temperature regularly every 4 hours.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Keep them hydrated with plenty of fluids.

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:24.000
Ensure they get adequate rest and sleep.

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Use fever-reducing medication if needed, as directed.

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:36.000
Seek medical attention if fever persists or worsens.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:42.000
Call emergency services for severe symptoms like difficulty breathing.
